That's a config issue, the configuration requires this line (in extra/httpd-manual.conf);

AliasMatch ^/manual(?:/(?:de|en|es|fr|ja|ko|pt-br|ru|tr))?(/.*)?$ "C:/Program Files (x86)/Apache Software Foundation/Apache2.2/manual$1"

which then collapses the respective /en/en/ to simply /en/.  Is this not working for you?
